rComments: he definitely knows his stuff, there is no doubt. however he does a rather poor job of explaining concepts. perhaps for soft courses like ast101 his mumbles doesnt get into the way of communicating the idea, BUT when its a 2 page derivation with extra hard physics, you will not understand a single thing he is saying. tests were hard.

Dr. Mochnacki knows his stuff. He sometimes mumbles and in the vastness of con hall his voice can get lost. However his lecture slides had excellent information and was available to answer questions after the lecture and during office hours so if you were unclear during the lecture he would clarify for you afterwards. He knows his stuff.
